level 3:
	spirit seeker
		new ritual only spell list
			beast sense
			speak with animals
	totem spirit:
		when raging:
			resistance to all damage but psychic

level 6:
	aspect of the beast
		conditional str check advantage
			pushing, pulling, lifting, breaking
		carrying capacity * 2

level 10:
	new spell for ritual-only spell list
		commune with nature

level 14:
	totemic attunement:
		when raging:
			if foe beside you AND can see and hear you AND isn't immune to being frightened
				has disadvantage on attacks against other targets
